         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ [Now that I have heard from Dr Müeller, to whom I forwarded two of your specimens, I am happy to inform you that I was right about the weed which you said had been lately introduced into your garde...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">73.01.00b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To William Woolls</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.1665in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.1665in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found. The text given here is an extract from a letter from Woolls to E. P. Ramsay, 13 January 1873 (</seg>ML MSS.563/3 E. P. Ramsay papers, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney). M’s letter is dated on the assumption that Woolls would have written to Ramsay soon after receiving it.</p>
               </note>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[Now that I have heard from Dr Müeller, to whom I forwarded two of your specimens, I am happy to inform you that I was right about the weed which you said had been lately introduced into your garden. It is "<seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">
                     <name key="Cleome">Cleome</name>
                  </hi>
               </seg>". I was also right in referring your Cape shrub to "<seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Ehretia</hi>
               </seg>": it is "<seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">E. Hottentotica</hi>
               </seg>!" [...]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.1665in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.1665in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Passage unrelated to M omitted.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> The Dr does not refer to your application, so I suppose nothing is settled.]</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Cleome">Cleome</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
